    "main": "There's nothing quite like losing yourself in your favourite tunes. The Digital Sound Enhancement Engine on these Sony headphones restores the harmonics that are lost during music compression, so your tunes sound more authentic. And with Multi-Point Connection, you can seamlessly switch between 2 Bluetooth devices - go from watching a movie on your tablet to taking a call on your phone. Simple!",
